title: Episode 154: Top Bitch (Feat. Don Q & Kendra Sunderland)
itunes:title: Episode 154: Top Bitch (Feat. Don Q & Kendra Sunderland)
description:
Rapper Don Q and porn star Kendra Sunderland join the ladies of Lip Service this week. Kendra, the 'top bitch' of Blacked.com, takes us through her journey as a porn star. Don Q confesses his love for Angela Yee, while opening up about his wrongdoings in past relationships. By the way...Don Q had no idea what he got himself into. Enjoy!
